 This\n6\t-- silently broke recall for any Chinese phrase shoвҖҰ","sessionId":"6465f3b1-7a6f-4cc3-a253-69841fb1326d","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"call_01_IH1b5R9aQScxkjoYqPEK9555\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-04T07:11:14.234Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mq6g5ro9_72c244cbeee0":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mq6g5ro9_72c244cbeee0","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"call_00_ckDNkYUwf8hcG503DljL8289\"} | 1\t-- Migration 014: Add FTS5 full-text search index for wiki_pages\n2\t--\n3\t-- Why: Q&A retrieval and Compile Discovery currently dump the ENTIRE\n4\t-- wiki_pages summary list to the LLM on every call. At ~1000 pages this\n5\t-- approaches 40k tokens per request. FTS5 lets us pre-filter to ~30\n6\t-- candidates in SQL before the AI ever sees them.\n7\t--\nвҖҰ","sessionId":"6465f3b1-7a6f-4cc3-a253-69841fb1326d","subtitle":"{\"toolUseId\":\"call_00_ckDNkYUwf8hcG503DljL8289\"}","timestamp":"2026-06-04T07:11:14.236Z","title":"post_tool_use","type":"other"},"obs_mq6g5ro9_7d2323ff4984":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mq6g5ro9_7d2323ff4984","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"symbol\":\"wiki_ask\",\"projectPath\":\"/Users/macbook/llmwiki/openwiki\",\"includeCode\":true}","sessionId":"6465f3b1-7a6f-4cc3-a253-69841fb1326d","subtitle":"{\"symbol\":\"wiki_ask\",\"projectPath\":\"/Users/macbook/llmwiki/openwiki\",\"includeCode\":true}","timestamp":"2026-06-04T07:11:19.835Z","title":"mcp__codegraph__codegraph_node","type":"other"},"obs_mq6g5ro9_fd22871ac684":{"concepts":[],"confidence":0.3,"facts":[],"files":[],"id":"obs_mq6g5ro9_fd22871ac684","importance":5,"narrative":"{\"toolUseId\":\"call_00_BmxXRRLEnRwK9V1t3WVK2486\"} | [{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"## wiki_ask (function)\\n\\n**Location:** src-tauri/src/commands/wiki.rs:129\\n**Signature:** `(\\n    state: State<'_, AppState>,\\n    session_id: String,\\n    question: String,\\n) -> Result<serde_json::Value, String>`\\n\\n```rust\\npub asyn